#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Entirely disables the use of HTTP for S/MIME."
msgstr "Deaktiverer helt brugen af HTTP til S/MIME."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, disableHTTPCB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Do not perform any HTTP requests"
msgstr "Udfør ingen HTTP-anmodninger"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, ignoreHTTPDPCB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When looking for the location of a CRL, the to-be-tested certificate usually "
"contains what are known as \"CRL Distribution Point\" (DP) entries, which "
"are URLs describing the way to access the CRL. The first-found DP entry is "
"used.  With this option, all entries using the HTTP scheme are ignored when "
"looking for a suitable DP."
msgstr ""
"Under søgning efter en CRL's placering indeholder certifikatet, der skal "
"testes, normalt, hvad der kaldes indgange for \"CRL distributionspunkter\" "
"(DP), som er URL'er, der beskriver måden at tilgå CRL'en. Den først fundne "
"DP-indgang bruges. Alle indgange, der bruger HTTP-skemaet, ignoreres med "
"dette tilvalg, når der søges efter et passende DP."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, ignoreHTTPDPCB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Ignore HTTP CRL distribution point of certificates"
msgstr "Ignorér certifikaters HTTP CRL-distributionspunkter"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QRadioButton, honorHTTPProxyRB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the value of the HTTP proxy shown on the right "
"(which comes from the environment variable http_proxy) will be used for any "
"HTTP request."
msgstr ""
"Hvis dette vælges, bruges HTTP-proxyen, der vises til højre (den kommer fra "
"miljøvariablen http_proxy) til enhver HTTP-anmodning."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, honorHTTPProxyRB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Use system HTTP proxy:"
msgstr "Brug systemets HTTP-proxy:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, useCustomHTTPProxyRB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Use this proxy for HTTP requests: "
msgstr "Brug denne proxy til HTTP-anmodninger: "

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QLineEdit, customHTTPProxy)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>If no system proxy is set, or you need to use a different proxy for "
"GpgSM, you can enter its location here.</p><p>It will be used for all HTTP "
"requests relating to S/MIME.</p><p>The syntax is host:port, for instance "
"myproxy.nowhere.com:3128.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Hvis ingen systemproxy er angivet eller hvis du skal bruge en anden proxy "
"til GpgSM, kan du angive dens placering her.</p><p>Den vil brugt til alle "
"HTTP-anmodninger, der er relaterede til S/MIME.</p><p> Syntaksen er "
"vært:port som f.eks minproxy.ingensteder.com:3128.</p>"

#. i18n: ectx: attribute (title), widget (QWidget, tabLDAP)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "&LDAP Requests"
msgstr "&LDAP-anmodninger"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, disableLDAPCB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Entirely disables the use of LDAP for S/MIME."
msgstr "Deaktivere helt brugen af LDAP til S/MIME."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, disableLDAPCB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Do not perform any LDAP requests"
msgstr "Udfør ingen LDAP-forespørgsler"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, ignoreLDAPDPCB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When looking for the location of a CRL, the to-be-tested certificate usually "
"contains what are known as \"CRL Distribution Point\" (DP) entries, which "
"are URLs describing the way to access the CRL. The first found DP entry is "
"used.  With this option, all entries using the LDAP scheme are ignored when "
"looking for a suitable DP."
msgstr ""
"Under søgning efter en CRL's placering indeholder certifikatet, der skal "
"testes, normalt, hvad der kaldes indgange for \"CRL distributionspunkter\" "
"(DP), som er URL'er, der beskriver måden at tilgå CRL'en. Den først fundne "
"DP-indgang bruges. Alle indgange, der bruger LDAP-skemaet, ignoreres med "
"dette tilvalg, når der søges efter et passende DP."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, ignoreLDAPDPCB)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Ignore LDAP CRL distribution point of certificates"
msgstr "Ignorér certifikaters LDAP CRL-distributionspunkter"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, customLDAPLabel)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid "Primary host for LDAP requests:"
msgstr "Primær vært for LDAP-forespørgsler:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QLineEdit, customLDAPProxy)
#: src/conf/smimevalidationconfigurationwidget.ui
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Entering an LDAP server here will make all LDAP requests go to that server "
"first. More precisely, this setting overrides any specified host and port "
"part in a LDAP URL and will also be used if host and port have been omitted "
"from the URL. Other LDAP servers will be used only if the connection to the "
"\"proxy\" failed.\n"
"The syntax is \"HOST\" or \"HOST:PORT\". If PORT is omitted, port 389 "
"(standard LDAP port) is used."
msgstr ""
"Angivelse af en LDAP-server her får alle LDAP-forespørgsler til først at gå "
"til denne server. Mere præcist tilsidesætter denne indstilling enhver "
"angivet værts- og port-del i en LDAP-URL, og bruges ligeledes hvis vært og "
"port er blevet udeladt i URL'en. Andre LDAP-servere bruges kun, hvis "
"forbindelsen til \"proxyen\" fejler.\n"
"Syntaxen er \"HOST\" eller \"HOST:PORT\". Hvis PORT udelades, bruges port "
"389 (standard LDAP-port)."

